'''1917年大西洋飓风季'''确认存在九个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，其中四个曾经[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]<ref name="documentation">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930195553/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | title = Documentation of Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Changes in HURDAT | author = Christopher W. Landsea | date = 2012-12 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-09 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] | display-authors = etal | archivedate = 2015-09-30 }}</ref>。7月6日，本季第一个天气系统在[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]以东海域出现，经过群岛和[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]并先后吹袭[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]、[[伯利兹|伯利兹]]及[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]，再于7月14日逐渐消散。接下来[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]进入沉寂，直到三个多星期后才有热带风暴在[[百慕大|百慕大]]成型。气旋掠过[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]东部，[[南塔克特|南塔克特]]附近有四艘船只沉没，导致41人遇难。风暴产生的大风还对[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]构成破坏，最终于8月10日转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。

8月30日，中[[大西洋|大西洋]]上空形成飓风，之后在百慕大东侧经过期间引起海潮高涨。除此以外风暴产生的影响很小，于9月5日转变成温带气旋。接下来形成的四个热带低气压都未能达到热带风暴强度，但随之而来的[[1917年新赫罗纳飓风|第四号飓风]]非常强劲，最高强度达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的四级飓风标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}，对[[牙买加|牙买加]]、[[古巴|古巴]]和[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|美国墨西哥湾沿岸部分地区]]构成重创，并以[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[佛罗里达西北狭长地带|西北狭长地带]]灾情特别严重。整场风暴共导致35人遇难，损失数额至少有17万美元{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有损失数额均为1917年[[美元|美元]]价值。|group="注"}}。

这年飓风季的活跃程度还经累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]反映出来，数值为61<ref name="ACE">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | title = Atlantic Basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | date = 2014-02 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-09 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-04-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425073956/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高、持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高<ref>{{cite web |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-04-01 |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html }}</ref>。

